comments: Carter Jr. (ORL) and Towns (MIN) engage in marginal contact on the perimeter.  Carter Jr. extends his arms somewhat as they disengage and Towns draws attention to the contact.
Edwards (MIN) makes contact with Bamba's (ORL) arm that affects his ability to get to the pass.
Carter Jr. (ORL) initiates marginal contact with Edwards (MIN) as he turns following the pick.
Towns (MIN) cleanly blocks Suggs' (ORL) driving shot attempt.
Anthony (ORL) makes contact with Russell's (MIN) arm that affects his jump shot attempt.
McDaniels (MIN) makes incidental contact with Bamba's (ORL) hand/arm as both players reach for the ball and attempt the grab the rebound.
Suggs (ORL) briefly places a hand to the front of Edwards (MIN) at the start of the drive, and the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Suggs (ORL) makes marginal contact with Edwards' (MIN) body during his shooting motion that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Towns (MIN) and Bamba (ORL) make incidental lower body contact in anticipation of the rebound.
Towns (MIN) commits a take foul on Anthony (ORL).
